{"tid":34391,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚飲大左...同左個好朋友發生左關系","createTime":"2016-12-11T12:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T13:17:06.000Z","uid":10246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42d3d662d05a8f5430c4fa5f05cbe80c67f32168","tid":34391,"uid":10246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日女朋友去左日本旅行 <br />\n所以屋企得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住尋晚，我沖完涼 <br />\n發覺電話有十幾個misscall <br />\n原來我朋友岩岩比男友飛左 <br />\n喊哂口咁同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後傾左成個鐘電話 <br />\n佢忽然話：不如出來陪我飲酒？ <br />\n但係個陣已經成十一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我見屋企無咩人 <br />\n又懶出去 <br />\n就話：不如你上來啦 我屋企又齊酒 <br />\n有私人空間又慳錢 <br />\n於是佢就上左來... <br />\n我地青島，生力，百威，藍妹<br />\n咩都溝下來飲 <br />\n結果唔使一個鐘兩個已經醉醉地同好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然 <br />\n佢對眼水汪汪咁問我： <br />\n你可唔可以 錫我一淡？ <br />\n可能真係能成為密友大概總帶著愛 <br />\n我竟然諗都無諗就錫左落去 <br />\n結果我地越咀越激 <br />\n互相纏住大家條頸 <br />\n舌頭交纏住咁行左入我房 <br />\n一攤上床 <br />\n我地互相摷左陣大家就埋牙 <br />\n詳細就唔多講 <br />\n只可以講係幾開心 <br />\n大家都出左兩次先攬住訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家覺得好對唔住女朋友 <br />\n同埋覺得同佢既友誼變左質 <br />\n巴絲你地話點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18758bb60a3ec6ac1b8363d871b53a1a678c22be","tid":34391,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"又loop"},{"pid":"4a4f1de95f3204955fd16c20a33e6a703b4bab71","tid":34391,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"哦 關我撚事"},{"pid":"a89ecc42416098340940a516d56c7385e7b24f18","tid":34391,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"一個月睇十幾次"},{"pid":"f9a5c7ec7eb23083c0a609d24a5fcd9d3969467d","tid":34391,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"快過donald 侵"},{"pid":"6d4771365a3fbee7aa1be815268588b007cea386","tid":34391,"uid":23836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:35:50.000Z","msg":"閲"},{"pid":"ad4c8f8a23a5804b7f9f85ae541cae2b11c36ddf","tid":34391,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:38:43.000Z","msg":"頭幾次睇依d 文都扯扯地，依加無撚晒反應。<br />\n醫生，我係咪有事呀？"},{"pid":"240bfcc50f04bf37b5f9fa0985bd29f7a1582863","tid":34391,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:15:35.000Z","msg":"終於係LIHKG 都出現埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0fe5ba45f14c5962795a79364ed92a2c172de7","tid":34391,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭幾次睇依d 文都扯扯地，依加無撚晒反應。<br />\n醫生，我係咪有事呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}